What does the following code print?
```java
List<Integer> nums = List.of(1, 2, 3, 4, 5);
int result = nums.stream()
    .filter(n -> n % 2 == 0)
    .mapToInt(Integer::intValue)
    .sum();
System.out.println(result);
```

